OL,3,CPolice hunt persistent sex pest who
OL,4,C'sniffed victim's neck'
OL,6,FOfficers are hunting a man who
OL,7,Fsexually assaulted a woman in
OL,8,FWinchester.
OL,10,FThe victim, a 22-year-old woman,
OL,11,Freported being approached by a man in
OL,12,Fan alleyway shortly before 8am on
OL,13,FTuesday May 26th.
OL,15,FThe man persistently asked her
OL,16,Fquestions, hugged her and sniffed her
OL,17,Fneck, as she walked between Fox Lane
OL,18,Fand Stanmore Lane.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/3
