OL,3,CPolice hunt persistent sex pest who
OL,4,C'sniffed victim's neck'
OL,6,FThe man police want to speak to is
OL,7,Fdescribed as mixed race, aged 20 to
OL,8,F30, 5ft 8ins to 5ft 9ins, of medium /
OL,9,Fmuscular build, with dark brown curly
OL,10,Fhair.
OL,12,FHe spoke with a European accent.
OL,14,FOfficers would like to speak to anyone
OL,15,Fwho was in the area at the time who
OL,16,Fmay have information to assist the
OL,17,Finvestigation.
